      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to show you this absolute gem. It\u2019s in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been babied and is ready for a new home, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat more about it!",
