    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously garaged its entire life, protected from the elements and preserved in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather seats remain supple with no visible bolster wear, and the original 'new car' scent lingers. Every switch, button, and electronic feature functions with tactile precision. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, boasting a documented, comprehensive service history from the authorized dealer. The engine bay is detailed to a high standard, showing no signs of fluid leaks or corrosion. The factory alloy wheels are free of any curb rash and are wrapped in high-performance tires with nearly full tread. This is a rare opportunity to own a pinnacle example of this model, perfect for the discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
