    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of exceptional caliber, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This specimen represents the pinnacle of its class, boasting a flawless exterior and an interior that remains in pristine, showroom condition. Every mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure peak performance. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a collector-grade vehicle that defies the passage of time.",
