      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving naturally aspirated performance, featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six with its individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS system operating in peak synchronization. The chassis remains structurally flawless with zero subframe deformation, paired with a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a tight limited-slip differential. Every mechanical tolerance meets factory specifications, and the exterior finish retains its original depth and luster. With a cabin free of bolster wear and a comprehensive service history detailing preventative rod bearing and VANOS maintenance, this vehicle is a turn-key investment for the serious collector.",
